name: Mighty Purse Black Shimmer
description:
Say hello to The Mighty Purse.  An oh-so-chic purse (wristlet) that charges your phone!  Yes your phone, any phone, and your e-reader.  I-phone, Samsung, Blackberry, Android...any phone, any model.  And the best part is it's actually a good looking bag!  One you won't be ashamed to carry in public!

So how does it work?  Simply plug your bag via USB into your USB charging device, charge for 3-5 hours and you are ready to go.  It will hold it's charge for 2 full charge cycles, and if you don't use it you don't lose it.  Made of gorgeous 100%  leather, and available in orange, an amazing blue, fuchsia, patent leather black, gold, emerald, nude patent leather, and chestnut brown, throw this wristlet into your bag, or carry it alone for a night on the town.  Plus travel...I mean how much easier is travel now?!

name: Van Rycke Silver Je t'aime Love Poem Ring Necklace
description:
Poem Ring Necklace by Van Rycke. Fine silver chain necklace with medium sized circular ring pendant featuring engraved French notes around the border - Je t’aime passionnement, a la folie, beaucoup, un peu meaning I love you passionately, madly, a lot, a little.
 
Colour - Silver | Sterling Silver | Van Rycke signature plate on the clasp. | Disk Width - 2cm, Chain Length - 50 cm | Box included | Made in Paris.
 
One size fits all.

Colour - Silver | Sterling Silver | Chain Length - 50 cm, Pendant Diameter- 1cm | Box included | Made in Paris.

Colour - Silver | Sterling Silver | Chain Length - 50 cm, Pendant diameter - 1cm | Box included | Made in Paris.
